  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 0
    description: 'You are late. The Crimson Host does not observe our scheduling preferences.'
    nextOption: I was told to report here.
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 0
    description: 'You were told correctly. I am Commander Varis. You have been assigned to the forward post.'
    nextOption: What are my orders?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 0
    description: 'The Crimson Host has established a position at the grain ruins in the Vale''s centre. It needs to be removed before they fortify it.'
    nextOption: How many?
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 0
    description: 'Enough to be a problem. Not enough that you should need help — unless you are considerably less capable than your file suggests.'
    nextOption: I understand.
  - startTime: 0
    showTime: 0
    description: 'Good. Come back when the position is clear. Do not loot the dead until the area is secure.'
    nextOption: 
